@startuml
title SettingsScreen / EditableDropdown - Управление выпадающими списками

actor User as User
participant "SettingsScreen /\nEditableDropdown" as UI
participant "SettingsViewModel /\nShared Reference VM" as VM
participant "AddBrandUseCase /\nDeleteModelUseCase /\nAddLocationUseCase" as UC
participant "DefaultReferenceDataRepository" as REPO
participant "BrandDao / ModelDao /\nLocationDao" as DAO
participant "AppDatabase" as DB

== Добавление элемента ==

User -> UI: вводит название и нажимает "Добавить"
UI -> VM: onAddItemRequested(newItemName)
VM -> UC: invoke(name)
UC -> UC: validateNotEmptyAndUnique()

alt Duplicate/Invalid
    UC --> VM: emit ValidationFailure
    VM --> UI: show inline error
else Valid
    UC -> REPO: addItem(newEntity)
    REPO -> DAO: insertItem(entity)
    DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO brands/models/locations
    DB --> DAO: newId
    DAO --> REPO: success
    REPO --> UC: Result.Success
    UC --> VM: emit ItemAdded
    VM --> UI: update dropdown list
end

== Удаление элемента ==

User -> UI: выбирает элемент для удаления
UI -> VM: onDeleteItemRequested(id)
VM -> UC: invoke(id)
UC -> REPO: deleteItem(id)
REPO -> DAO: deleteItem(id)
DAO -> DB: DELETE FROM table WHERE id=?
DB --> DAO: rowsDeleted
DAO --> REPO: success
REPO --> UC: Result.Success
UC --> VM: emit ItemDeleted
VM --> UI: remove item from UI

@enduml